Hi Diane,

Sorry it took a day to get back to you.  Yes, it is funny the things we sometimes think we hear (or they say? lol).  I wasn&#39;t 100% sure it was &quot;foot in mouth&quot; - maybe &quot;food/put/ (something???) in mouth&quot;.  That&#39;s all.  It&#39;s tough to call something like that but there was clearly (to me) something being said that sounded that way between &quot;UFO&quot; and the laugh. Do you hear that?  I mean, do you hear anything in between?  It was in the same voice as I heard it....  hmm....  Maybe they&#39;re messing with me :).

Adrienne


